snippet.title: Amber Heard Was Cancer For Johnny Depp MGTOW
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Was Cancer For Johnny Depp MGTOW

MGTOW 101

It’s about that time that I revisited our old friends Johnny Depp and his divorce loving, gold digging cunt of an ex-wife,  Amber Heard. 
I was recently send an article by my good friend Adam which was written by a nasty feminist and she is obviously taking Amber Heard’s side. Trigger warning, massive cringe and f bombs ahead. 

So this article is titled: 
Amber Heard's Latest Divorce Issue Reveals a Greater Struggle Faced by Divorced Women
The article reads: 
"I want my life back."
That's one line from Amber Heard's request for order motion against ex-husband, Johnny Depp. She filed the motion because she claimed Depp has been holding her finances hostage. 
And so he should, Amber Turd was nothing but cancer on Johnny Depp, she was after his money and fame… Johnny was a real dumb ass to get married, let alone involved with this nasty gold digging bitch.
